<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ewr und
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>unser<ex>r</ex></expan> guten frewnde der stett
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>eynung</expan>
<expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan>, die gen Presslaw reiten
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>,<app>
<note><q type="date"> auf den ewichtag der
                                        <expan>weyhenn<ex>achten</ex></expan>
                                schierist</q>01.01.1420</note>
</app> zu <expan>Nördling<ex>en</ex></expan> sein und fürbas vollreiten
                                <expan>süll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntliche<ex>n</ex></expan> schrift mit fleiss und
                                <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                            <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        frewnde <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> rate daselbsthin gen Presslaw gefertigt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, die mitsampt
                            <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>reynische<ex>n</ex></expan> stette <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        botten, die zu uns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> warn,
                                <expan>newliche<ex>n</ex></expan> bey uns
                                <expan>auszgeritte<ex>n</ex></expan> sein. Und wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="cetula"><ab><p facs="#facs79">Cettula: <expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
